21:27.875 --> 21:29.208
[senyap] Pistol itu.

21:30.875 --> 21:35.541
Okey, uh, saya rasa kita semua
rasa tegang.

21:35.541 --> 21:37.041
Ya?

21:38.166 --> 21:40.666
Sedikit tekanan? [ketawa gementar]

21:40.666 --> 21:45.291
