22:22.041 --> 22:23.958
Tolong?

22:36.166 --> 22:38.083
Okey. Hebat.

22:38.083 --> 22:42.958
Eh, tangan diangkat pada kiraan ketiga. Bersedia?

22:42.958 --> 22:44.958
Satu...

22:46.041 --> 22:48.500
Dua...

22:49.916 --> 22:50.916
Tiga.

